1.SQL schema(According to how many paths needed in the app):

CREATE TABLE `Files` (
  `column1` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `column2` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `column3` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `column4` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `column5` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `column6` datetime DEFAULT NULL
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1

2.host_to_ping.txt :
    What host you want to ping(KODI-Client)

3.paths.txt
    path of folder you want to check if changed since last update in DB 

4.credentials.txt:
    connection details and username,password & DB name:
    localhost
    username
    password
    db_name
